skdetail:

Invocation Name: city bikes
des:
Find the nearest city bike station with bikes available. Skill works in HSL area and finds city bikes from Helsinki and Espoo.

Skill needs access to device address for finding closest bike station. Allow permissions when installing or after first skill activation.

Find skill handler source code from GitHub
https://github.com/vaahtokarkki/alexa-city-bikes
